title: Pacific Rental
posting_body: ["Just what you've been waiting for!", 'This large 5 Bdrm 3 bath home sits on over an acre and lives like 2 homes!', 'Separate entrance to lower level w/full kitchen provides multiple living opportunities!', 'Over 3200 SQ FT!', 'Well kept w/recent new carpeting, paint, front door heating/cooling.', 'Formal living rm w/fireplace, dinning rm, spacious kitchen w/lots of counter space, large master w/bath, in house vac, downstairs 2nd kitchen, bonus room, 2 beds, bath, sun-room and hello...a 1200 sq/ft detached garage!', 'Get approved quickly so you can live in this beautiful home.', 'In order to qualify for the Rent To Own Program:', '• You must have at least $85,000 in Combined Gross Household Income', '•', 'A minimum FICO score of 620', '• No evictions in the past 3 years', '• Takes 5-6 weeks from start to finish', 'We work with previous bankruptcies, foreclosures and short sales!', 'There is a 1 time $75 application fee, which is good for the whole household, and for any of our qualifying houses!', 'You must be pre-approved to view any available properties.', 'Pet Friendly!', 'Up to 3 cats/dogs OKAY!', '(Due to extreme insurance liability, we cannot allow Dobermans, Pitbulls, Rottweilers or Mastiffs)', 'Contact me today for more information and details about the program!', "The home in the picture is an example of what you could get, it's not this home in particular.", '•\tdo NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers', 'Kristin Hood', 'Keller Williams Lake Tapps']
